EC2
EC2 Instance Configuration for 100-200 Students
Recommended Instance Type:
t3.large (2 vCPU, 8 GB RAM) - Good starting point

t3.xlarge (4 vCPU, 16 GB RAM) - Better for peak loads

c5.xlarge (4 vCPU, 8 GB RAM) - CPU optimized for better performance

Storage & Network:
EBS Volume: 50-100 GB gp3 SSD

Security Group: HTTP (80), HTTPS (443), SSH (22)

Load Balancer: Application Load Balancer for high availability

